item.title: CVE-2018-25030|2024-08-05T12:26:39.623Z -- mirmay -- secure%20private%20browser
item.description: A vulnerability classified as problematic has been found in Mirmay Secure Private Browser and File Manager up to 2.5. Affected is the Auto Lock. A race condition leads to a local authentication bypass. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
